<edge_case_handling>

| Condition | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| No workflow detected | Ask user to specify: `spec`, `tm`, or `plan` |
| No tasks found | Output <no_tasks_remaining> block and STOP |
| Validation failure | STOP, report error, ask user how to proceed |
| `--auto` encounters error | STOP, report error, do NOT continue to next task |

</edge_case_handling>

<constraints>

- Output ONLY the structured execution manifest — no prose, no summaries
- ALWAYS run validation after direct execution
- ALWAYS create commits automatically after validation passes
- STOP on validation failure (do not auto-continue in `--auto` mode)
- For TDD tasks, use `/spec.cycle` instead

</constraints>

